dc_title_s: Geologic atlas of Goodhue County, Minnesota, C-12, Part B, Plate 10, Sinkholes, Sinkhole Probability, and Springs and Seeps
dc_description_s: Maps showing distribution of karst (carbonate rock with caves, springs) units and features and karst hydrology in carbonate rocks susceptible to being dissolved by acidic ground water, scale 1:100000, Goodhue County.
dc_publisher_s: Minnesota Department of Natural Resources, Division of Waters
